    <thetext>Created attachment 1110721
pidgin-birthday-reminder.metainfo.xml

According to the packaging guidelines every package that provides an add-on to a GUI app should ship an AppStream metafile. See https://fedoraproject.org/wiki/Packaging:AppData
This package is missing one. I&apos;ve created it for you, see the attachment.

The upstream project has also been moved to a new address: https://github.com/kgraefe/pidgin-birthday-reminder and there is a newer version.

I&apos;ve already put the new address in the metafile, but the spec file should also be fixed and the packaged updated to the newest version upstream.</thetext>
